<h2 data-nh-numbering="1.2. ">Overview</h2>
<p>
    This page documents the SAP Block checks (Export Compliance, Order, Billing and Delivery blocks) that R4C
    evaluates during Case creation and Case edit, for every party level involved in a Return for Credit case: Sold To,
    Payer and Ship To.
</p>
<p>
    <strong>Purpose:</strong> Give Developers and QA a single, accurate reference for which block fields are checked,
    at which party/level, what values are treated as hard stops, and how the system behaves differently between Case
    creation and Case edit.
</p>
