    <ac:rich-text-body>
        <p>
            This section used to be duplicated across the Admin, Exception, Quality, Stock Rotation and Technical
            intake pages. It is now maintained in one place. Intake pages should link to this page for block logic
            instead of repeating it: if a block rule changes, it only needs to be updated here.
        </p>
    </ac:rich-text-body>
</ac:structured-macro>
